      "text": [
        "2160 - وَ قَالَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : « اَلرُّكْنُ اَلْيَمَانِيُّ بَابُنَا اَلَّذِي نَدْخُلُ مِنْهُ اَلْجَنَّةَ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2160 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said: \"The Yemeni Corner is our gate through which we enter Paradise.\""
        ]
      }
    }
